# Apple Touch Icon (180x180)
# This should be a PNG file for iOS home screen icons
# Use the favicon.svg and convert it to a 180x180 PNG using:
# convert -background white -flatten favicon.svg -resize 180x180 apple-touch-icon.png
# 
# Or use an online SVG to PNG converter at:
# https://convertio.co/svg-png/
# https://cloudconvert.com/svg-to-png
